text: pitabrakd nasa puok del ban brachheang ning ban reareang anak dtei pi meakra robsa a l laoh haeyning ban brachheang nung anakneasar banteabpi meankar changaoulobangheanh ban banhcheak yeang chbasa haey noh puokke min ach bangk krohthnak avei dl a l laoh laey . haey trong nung loubbambat ampeula robsa puokke
